{"tid":272,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚熱愛淘寶的親[1]轉會啦喂","createTime":"2016-11-25T14:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T14:11:54.000Z","uid":2646,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf9221ca12478df6c2c21b5b7f96f22c5f517ee5","tid":272,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:35:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我地並冇開WHATSAPP GROUP,只係有個CD ROM巴打騎劫,借淘寶分享搵食,已經有巴打PM我,入面講淫野/叫雞多過淘寶。最後講多次:「我地並冇開WHATSAPP GROUP」</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>此POST如有集運內容,未必與開POST者有關,ADMIN如要BAM人,請小心處理,勿亂BAM!!!! </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>屌你班仆街咪撚再講集運,講撚到POST都比人DEL撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想問/講集運去呢到</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CO&amp;amp;message=6545226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum9.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Ftype%3DCO%26amp%3Bmessage%3D6545226&d=N1YZ8xns4N%2B4Etv8Z6OrbidsDnU63rC4p1%2FkKkYWdPQ%3D&h=df6d73aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum9.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?type=CO&amp;amp;message=6545226</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">國內運可以講但到左集運倉之後就去集運POST問/講</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">陳年淘寶excel link</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1U44KJhCAiLEGvVjh_KM0lWLplxQnTDymgf1oh4pZwmM/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1U44KJhCAiLEGvVjh_KM0lWLplxQnTDymgf1oh4pZwmM%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=N1YZ8xns4N%2B4Etv8Z6OrbidsDnU63rC4p1%2FkKkYWdPQ%3D&h=a22c8efe\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1U44KJhCAiLEGvVjh_KM0lWLplxQnTDymgf1oh4pZwmM/edit?usp=sharing</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"797670c4f339d4cd34bd28fd1daa2f9f36a398cf","tid":272,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"波兒已放棄大家,歡迎派膠 <br />\n已轉換文字為連結<a href=\"http://forum1.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=290065\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fforum1.hkgolden.com%2FProfilePage.aspx%3Fuserid%3D290065&d=N1YZ8xns4N%2B4Etv8Z6OrbidsDnU63rC4p1%2FkKkYWdPQ%3D&h=b3cee094\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum1.hkgolden.com/ProfilePage.aspx?userid=290065</a> <br />\n波兒派膠處<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新手請睇左以下需知先 <br />\n此帖用於：分享你淘寶既野，毒害一眾巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n從而令佢地大灑金錢 出完糧未到月中已經要捱麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自此跌入淘寶呢個無底深淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">關於集運及付款等問題咪撚再係到問，尊重下大家及自己，自己GOOGLE下爬下文就有答案，請巴絲打們亦唔好再答，無謂助長伸手歪風</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n集運及各項淘撚基本需知 <br />\n- GOOGLE打「淘 高登 (你想問既野) 」 或 「淘 (你想問既野)」 <br />\n然後就可以爬文得到詳盡既答案，快撚過你等人履你履過九萬幾次既答案喇屌！ <br />\n<br />\n- 如果GOOGLE都嫌麻撚煩？唔緊要，落樓下飛的去買你想要既野，即日買到，仲洗硬膠膠等速遞咩 <br />\n<br />\n- 若果GOOGLE爬曬文咁叻叻豬都找唔到答案先再發問，無巴絲會怪你既，實會耐心解答 <br />\n<br />\n現呼籲巴絲打們請勿再解答任何有關集運的基本問題 , 此風不可長！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n親愛的主呀 ,你賜給的淘寶讓我們消費 <br />\n使我們豐足,你賜給的時間讓我們虛耗 <br />\n使我們豐盛,,主呀,請你全能地救助我地 <br />\n拯救我們,脫離凶惡, <br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀， <br />\n全是你的，直到永遠！阿們。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n=========================<br />\n**波兒大嗚大悲咒 <br />\n淘寶,淘寶,請賜予魔法給我,令人大灑金錢 <br />\n以至包都無得食, 窮到要做乞衣 <br />\n淘寶賜我力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"c4ff17bcbdb51d874e866ce98345ac59aad61df9","tid":272,"uid":2646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">付款問題,蠢撚/盲撚唔識既話唔好淘喇<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.alicdn.com/tps/TB1enbHLpXXXXXqXVXXXXXXXXXX-1400-300.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.alicdn.com%2Ftps%2FTB1enbHLpXXXXXqXVXXXXXXXXXX-1400-300.png&h=c963100f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://world.taobao.com/markets/all/payment_hk?spm=a21bp.7806943.banner_HK_user.13.71CdQW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.taobao.com%2Fmarkets%2Fall%2Fpayment_hk%3Fspm%3Da21bp.7806943.banner_HK_user.13.71CdQW&d=N1YZ8xns4N%2B4Etv8Z6OrbidsDnU63rC4p1%2FkKkYWdPQ%3D&h=45bf5fd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://world.taobao.com/markets/all/payment_hk?spm=a21bp.7806943.banner_HK_user.13.71CdQW</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有傳2016年7月1日起支付寶又有實名認證<br />\n未來蠢撚將不能淘寶</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2016年10月13日起,支付寶HK正式推出 <br />\n根據官方消息,將會免手續費至2017年4月 <br />\n詳情:<a href=\"https://world.taobao.com/markets/all/alipayhk_intro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fworld.taobao.com%2Fmarkets%2Fall%2Falipayhk_intro&d=N1YZ8xns4N%2B4Etv8Z6OrbidsDnU63rC4p1%2FkKkYWdPQ%3D&h=a5aee9e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://world.taobao.com/markets/all/alipayhk_intro</a></span><br />\n<br />\n成日有人PM問點解唔可以連埋集運一齊講<br />\n你問野緊係覺得冇問題啦,但呢個POST你估真係得淘寶既人咩?<br />\n呢到有記者/團購公司/集運公司/CD ROM<br />\n<br />\n你問集運野,問問下就會多人討論自己用邊間/邊間好,之後集運公司既打手就會打晒飛機咁宣傳自己間野,<br />\n跟住,其他公司可能眼紅對手,report比admin,admin有時唔係刪一個留言,而係全個POST刪左,同BAM開POST果位,所以我地先咁反對人係呢到講集運。(以前已經有幾個無辜既巴打被BAM)"},{"pid":"f0c67977e3c2bfcc5157a9ba8ad9cc19eac50590","tid":272,"uid":2102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:36:34.000Z","msg":"輕鬆留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2420b3fc2380ec7c5bc2744de22b60ba24431634","tid":272,"uid":1900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"793a830b9ac452165646838f45ea7f34d5ffdfdc","tid":272,"uid":2390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"以為再冇機會見到淘寶post鳥，好感動呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cbd35bea3fde47a86ad81c6b6c2ea0d8ab4affa","tid":272,"uid":1797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:38:54.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多 即刻留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e7f8e0782d807c60384d40da8b66d1da3b4021","tid":272,"uid":1630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41eb07df52b7a38fe33dbc381947816fce5d4760","tid":272,"uid":2308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-25T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmcq21ZzYJFzqa8HgMJ5hHgL5q8UgvoiSypgxiHhZjEwma?filename=j0eNCJ.jpg\" data-thumb